  "title": "HR Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle payroll calculation, tax submission &amp; etc</li>\n  <li>Handle recruitment such as job posting, selection, interview &amp; etc</li>\n  <li>Handle onboarding &amp; offboarding process</li>\n  <li>Handle foreign work pass application</li>\n  <li>Assist in the communication, interpretation, and all other HR related matters.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accuracy in the maintenance of manpower records in the system</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties as required or assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
